OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782505102
OL,3,CSchool closed following lightning
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,FA school in North Tyneside has been
OL,7,Fforced to close after being struck by
OL,8,Flightning.
OL,10,FChurchill Community College in
OL,11,FWallsend announced it will close its
OL,12,Fdoors today (Friday 26 June) following
OL,13,Fthe strike, which caused damage to its
OL,14,Felectrical systems.
OL,16,FA statement posted on the school's
OL,17,Fwebsite read "Unfortunately due to a
OL,18,Flightening strike this morning,
OL,19,Fcausing damage to our school
OL,20,Felectrical systems we are closed today.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
