OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782505102
OL,3,CSchool closed following lightning
OL,4,Cstrike
OL,6,F"We will provide further updates, but
OL,7,Fanticipate school should be open on
OL,8,FMonday as usual."
OL,10,FThe closure followed widespread
OL,11,Fthunderstorms across the North East on
OL,12,FFriday morning following three days of
OL,13,Fhot and humid weather.
OL,15,FA thunderstorm warning remains in
OL,16,Fplace across the North East until 9pm.
OL,18,FThere have been reports of flash
OL,19,Fflooding overnight in Whitby on the
OL,20,FNorth Yorkshire coast.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
